parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The spontaneous cracking of the windshield can impede the driver's vision, leading to accidents or other safety hazards. The cracking can also cause the windshield to shatter, which can lead to injury or further damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: often without any visible impact or warning signs. The cracks can start from the bottom of the windshield
or from the deicer area. The cracks can spread rapidly
often within a short period of time.
